00:04:54.980 --> 00:05:01.459
shopping. Are we off the clock, so to speak, because we're no longer in the formal preaching work?

00:05:02.819 --> 00:05:07.779
We don't look at it that way. When we're at the grocery store, we're still on the lookout for

00:05:07.779 --> 00:05:13.540
people we can share the good news with. We may be able to talk to someone standing next to us

00:05:13.540 --> 00:05:20.740
in a long checkout line, or perhaps with the clerk who processes our order. We can keep it simple.

00:05:21.699 --> 00:05:26.899
