00:05:48.180 --> 00:05:55.699
shopping, or on public transportation. Here's an idea. Why not have a small supply of contact

00:05:55.699 --> 00:06:03.149
cards or other literature with you wherever you go? We've said that we're ready to share the good

00:06:03.149 --> 00:06:11.550
news wherever we find people. But what about the people we don't find? Those who are often not at home.

00:06:13.389 --> 00:06:17.629
